Lustre must be mounted as /mnt/lustre before running setup step and tests.

cd scripts/regression

On a scratch test system, run:
./1-test-setup.sh
* creates and configure robinhood database
* register a client for reading changelogs
* start posix copytool

Lustre-HSM PolicyEngine tests:
	for brief output:
		./2-run-tests.sh -q
	for full output:
		./2-run-tests.sh

To run other Lustre-HSM tests:
	./3-tests-lustre.sh
